{"tid":970737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★匈牙利示威抗議放寬OT時數 形容是「奴隸法」。","createTime":"2019-01-06T05:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T09:48:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08a0c2dde4854d1e91ad790f39fbc75a2332bc0c","tid":970737,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】匈牙利有大型示威抗議政府通過新勞工法。<br />\n<br />\n超過一萬名示威者在首都布達佩斯遊行，又在國會大樓外舉行集會，抗議政在上個月通過新的勞工法，放寬加班時數上限，容許僱主要求僱員每年最多可以加班四百小時，惹來工會烈抨擊，形容新勞工法是剝削工人的「奴隸法」。<br />\n<br />\n發起遊行示威的工會要求總理歐爾班落實增加薪酬及改善退休制度，又警告如果政府不回應訴求，他們會號召支持者發起全國罷工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=333178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D333178&d=mSCPsj%2BCpXNT31el%2F4C9KnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=8ed97a83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D333178&h=f0c8a7a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=333178</a>"},{"pid":"7ae755f20af6fc1a24d2ae98297f52b5b0571538","tid":970737,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"why not HK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5f98f4645578d84e17f1214993e696b092c23c","tid":970737,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"香港僱主: 歡迎新法例, 可提高生產力及更靈活地分配工作給員工"},{"pid":"022b08ac07c87ca6cfed60ac2c2d01cb84ebf345","tid":970737,"uid":103759,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:44:44.000Z","msg":"強烈要求香港成立OT法案 每日最少OT多8個鐘 如果唔係公司同員工都係犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b016b237f291ac456d0b5b1726427330cb7f892b","tid":970737,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"022